      },
      "date": "2014-03-14 21:13:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\n(4 comments)\n\nI see now that lu_fid_diff() is only used in the osp/osp_precreate.c file, and this function is not safe for comparing FIDs sent remotely.  It might be OK for use inside OSP since it knows that the FIDs are only from the one OST.\n\nIn this case, I'd suggest to move lu_fid_diff() into osp_precreate.c so that it isn't accidentally used in the OFD code where it would cause a DOS.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
